      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Sir I mention the above so that you will not think an idiot",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "is writing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "You seemingly do not know or utterly disregard the following",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "subject. I had hoped that you might make a statement before",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "now on this subject. I have waited many years to see your",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "opinion in print, but nothing of the sort has happened.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "I am speaking of the UFO's or unidentified flying objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "before long and it is a matter of time you are going to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "scooped so to speak on this subject. Sir I happen to know",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "they exist. I have personally seen two of them. One of these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "sightings under low cloud cover in daylight. (I am not sure",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "of the cloud height). The other at perhaps two thousand",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "feet altitude and appx.one mile off.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "You may not be interested ? But I think this may be vital to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "the security of the United States and if it is vital I am",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "sure that you are now familiar with and working on this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "problem.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "If I am correct and these things do land I am greatly con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "-cerned as to what kind of reception they might receive from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
